high_descs: Take a small step forward then turn left and walk to the stove that's on your left and turn left to face it when you get to it.
Pick up the pan that's on the bottom right burner.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take two steps then turn right to face the coffee maker.
Put the pan to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the stove, turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the pot on the front right of the stove.
Turn left, bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Take the chilled pot from the fridge, turn around, bring the pot to the table on the right.
Put the chilled pot on the table in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the table in the front of the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the stove on the left.
Pick up the pot from the front right burner of the stove.
Carry the pot and turn to the left and then left again to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pot inside. Shut the door, then open it. Take the pot out and shut the door.
Carry the pot and turn around. Face the white table on the right.
Place the pot on the right side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot and place it on the table.
